		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
		<tr>
		    <td valign="top">
		     <p><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Article Title:</b>&nbsp;</font>
		     <font face="Verdana" size="2">New Bind Spots Locations</font><br>
		     <a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=386344" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></p>
			 </td>
		</tr>
		
		<tr><td>&nbsp;</tr><tr>
		
		    <td valign="top"><div style= "padding:4;float: right"> <script language=JavaScript src=http://www.obsidian-tech.com/absolutebm/abmx.aspx?z=26></script></div><p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    Checked a few message boards and the information appears to be accurate. Received from Jook:
<blockquote>
<p>
I was surprised there wasn't a note about the new bind spots so I though I might submit one.</p>
<p>
Anatonica - North Karana - Gypsy camp - 
Location about  Neg 1000, 0.</p>
<p>
Kunark - Frontier Mountains - Empty ruins
Location about Neg 2200, 1300.</p>
<p>
Kunark - Kaesora - Anywhere<br>
It seems that the whole zone might be bindable now, but I'd suggest only the entrance.</p>
<p>
Jook 38th Warrior<br>
Holy Redemption<br>
Bertox</p>
</blockquote>
		    </font></p>
			 </td>
